    <h1>Predictive Lead Scoring</h1>
    <p class="description">A machine learning approach that analyses historical CRM and behavioural data to <strong>rank leads by conversion probability</strong> — so sales teams prioritise the right prospects instead of working through an undifferentiated queue.</p>
    <div class="post-meta">
