              <span class="faq-toggle"><svg viewBox="0 0 12 12"><path d="M6 1v10M1 6h10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg></span>
            </button>
            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Traditional lead scoring assigns points based on marketing team assumptions — job title gets 10 points, downloaded a whitepaper gets 5 points. Predictive scoring uses machine learning on actual conversion data to find which signals really predict sales in your market. Predictive models typically outperform manual scoring by 20-40% in conversion rate accuracy.</p></div></div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
              <span class="faq-q-text">What data does predictive lead scoring need?</span>
              <span class="faq-toggle"><svg viewBox="0 0 12 12"><path d="M6 1v10M1 6h10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg></span>
            </button>
